    11	
    12	### Frontend (`static/js/schema.js`)
    13	- **Toggle system**: Binary switch between GraphViz (default) and Mermaid
    14	- **State management**: `useGraphviz` boolean, localStorage preferences
    15	- **Rendering functions**: `renderGraphvizSchema()` and `renderMermaidSchema()`
    16	- **Zoom/pan**: Universal `initializeZoomPan()` function for both modes
    17	- **Theme support**: Automatic light/dark theme switching
    18	- **Caching**: GraphViz results cached by theme to avoid re-generation
    19	
    20	### UI Structure (`templates/index.html`)
    21	- **Modal container**: `.schema-modal` with `.schema-content`
    22	- **Display elements**: `.mermaid` div and `#graphvizContent` img
    23	- **Controls**: `.schema-controls` with binary toggle switch
    24	- **Current toggle**: GraphViz ↔ Mermaid switch with labels
